properties.areaDesc: Juneau Borough and Northern Admiralty Island
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 24 at 4:44AM AKST until January 24 at 6:00PM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 3 to 6
inches.

* WHERE...Juneau Borough and Northern Admiralty Island.

* WHEN...From 9 AM this morning to 6 PM AKST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult. The hazardous
conditions could impact the morning or evening commute.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Snowfall rates could exceed 1 inch per hour
at times. This could make snow removal difficult during the
heavier snowfall.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM THIS MORNING TO 6 PM AKST THIS EVENING
